This is a tool to scrape the newest stock info for A-share market.

usage: stock_crawl.py [-h] [-i INPUT_FILE] [-o OUTPUT_DIR]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -i INPUT_FILE, --input_file INPUT_FILE
                        input file
  -o OUTPUT_DIR, --output_dir OUTPUT_DIR
                        output dir
